data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom 2.5 bath Cape Cod in sought after location, on a quiet Tree lined street just a couple blocks from Lockwood park. The 1st floor offers spacious Living Room, eat-in Kitchen, Master Bedroom Full Bath and 2nd bedroom. 2nd floor has a huge bedroom, a half bath and great attic storage. On the lower level there is a finished rec-room with a fireplace, another full bath and a toy room. Nice mostly fenced back yard with a big 2.5 car garage. **Updates include: Furnace and Central Air- 2023, Garage Roof- 2023, Bathroom Remodel- 2022, Roof-2009, & Windows-2007.
